### 13.5 Pause Rhythm

Where you stop shapes how we read urgency.

```scheme
;; Impatient — minimal hold, quick continuation
(motion
  (sequence
    (take 0.3 (shift (vec 0 0) (vec 40 0)))
    (hold 0.05)
    (take 0.3 (shift (vec 40 0) (vec 80 0)))))
```

[VISUAL: tap-tap rhythm, barely pauses]

```scheme
;; Deliberate — long hold, considered continuation
(motion
  (sequence
    (take 0.5 (shift (vec 0 0) (vec 40 0)))
    (hold 0.8)
    (take 0.5 (shift (vec 40 0) (vec 80 0)))))
```

