    (take 0.2 (shift (vec 0 0) (vec 0 -8)))
    (take 0.15 (shift (vec 0 -8) (vec 0 0)))
    (take 0.1 (shift (vec 0 0) (vec 0 -3)))
    (take 0.08 (shift (vec 0 -3) (vec 0 0)))))
```

[VISUAL: lands, pops up twice, settles light]

```scheme
;; Heavy damping — single bounce, quick stop
