  (sequence
    (take 0.5 (shift (vec 0 30) (vec 0 0)))
    (take 0.15 (shift (vec 0 0) (vec 0 -5)))
    (take 0.1 (shift (vec 0 -5) (vec 0 0)))))
```

[VISUAL: drops hard, one faint bounce, done]

Spring suggests youth or energy; damping suggests mass or fatigue.

